title: US bans Huawei, ZTE equipment sales amid Chinese spying fears
description: The Biden administration has banned approvals of new telecommunications equipment from China's Huawei Technologies and ZTE because they pose "an unacceptable risk" to US national security.

title: Taiwan votes in local elections billed as message for China and the world
description: Polls opened in Taiwan on Saturday in local elections that President Tsai Ing-wen has framed as being about sending a message to the world about the island's determination to defend its democracy in the face of China's rising bellicosity.

title: Speeding tanks, booming howitzers, shaking bones: This is how South Korea sells weapons
description: With a blinding yellow flash and a concussion that shakes bones, K9 self-propelled howitzers launch artillery shells onto a hill that's just been hit by rockets fired from helicopters. Then K2 tanks roar in, speeding up roads and firing as they go.
